title: Battle of the Box Presses!

description: Will Padron hold up at five times the cost of the Onyx? Is it really five time better? Find out today on The Cigar Authority! We also pay tribute to the troops as the men and women from the U.S. military stop by for a visit on their second annual Military Motorcycle Ride.
